## Key Features (MVP Phase 1)

1. **Conversational Goal Scoping** - AI-driven goal clarification
2. **Skill Assessment** - Contextual questions to determine learning level
3. **Personalized Curriculum Builder** - AI-generated learning paths
4. **Learning Journey Dashboard** - Visual progress tracking
5. **Dynamic Learning Adaptation** - Pace adjustment based on performance
6. **AI Learning Assistant** - Inline chat for concept clarification
7. **User Authentication & Persistence** - Progress saving and user profiles

